dc_description_s: Issued by the State Automobile Insurance Association. Includes place name index on recto. Advertisements and 'Section of transcontinental highway map' showing the United States south of a line from Bangor, Maine to Wahpeton, North Dakota and east of a line from Limon, Colorado to Sanderson, Texas on verso. Scale 1:860,000. Engravers and publishers, the George F. Cram Company.
